name: TimeFree Innovations
overview:
TimeFree Innovations is a software development company based in the Philippines.

The company is the developer of TimeFree, a virtual queuing system with text notification functionality.

TimeFree provides businesses with an efficient queuing solution that promotes an environment of positive customer experiences. In addition to this, TimeFree gives customers of businesses the freedom on how to spend their wait time. With TimeFree, a customer no longer has to be stuck in a long queue waiting for his turn. He can simply use the system to be in a virtual queue so he can leave the establishment, do other things he wants to do, and just receive a text alert if his turn is about to come.
